            <p class="- topic/p " xtrc="p:4;71:16" xtrf="file:/C:/Users/Filip/Desktop/-Screenshots-best-practices/Topics/Ho%20to%20create%20a%20perfect%20screenshot/t_how%20to_4_editing.dita">✅ Figure out precisely what you are doing the screenshots for, and capture just
                the details you need. Take some time to make sure that no UI element will be left
                outside the frame if it is of importance. A user should understand where the element
                in question is located in the UI to be able to find it.<simpletable class="- topic/simpletable " frame="none" id="simpletable_isf_3dv_ktb" relcolwidth="1* 1*" xtrc="simpletable:3;75:70" xtrf="file:/C:/Users/Filip/Desktop/-Screenshots-best-practices/Topics/Ho%20to%20create%20a%20perfect%20screenshot/t_how%20to_4_editing.dita">
